    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<strong>真格斗，更良心！</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2339300/extras/7cea88049a7c340a483e2f8b483f8d77.poster.avif?t=1716944278\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2339300/extras/7cea88049a7c340a483e2f8b483f8d77.webm?t=1716944278\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2339300/extras/7cea88049a7c340a483e2f8b483f8d77.mp4?t=1716944278\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>派对之星再次带来月之暗面大版本更新：全新一批多彩贴纸、每周限免英雄、社区赛事奖杯墙……欢乐又刺激的格斗派对仍在继续！<br>《派对之星》是一款平台格斗游戏。在这里，你将使用最有趣的英雄，在派对进行精彩对决。攻击、跳跃、闪避、防御……花式玩法，将敌人击出场外！找到属于你的战斗风格，下一个派对之星就是你！<br><br><strong>【胜利方式】</strong><br>在派对中赢得胜利的方式很简单，只需把其他人都从舞台中击飞！攻击其他玩家的英雄，会增加英雄头顶上方的击飞值，击飞值越高，受到攻击时约容易被击飞。<br><br><strong>【多种英雄】</strong><br>圆滚滚的雪人、从天而降的神界试炼官、脑袋变成苹果形状的女高中生和万众瞩目的偶像歌姬，这些风格迥异的原创角色都已经加入了《派对之星》的战斗！当然，还有来自独立动作游戏《艾希》的全新英雄，以及来自玩家设计的镰鼬少女……超过二十名各具特色的英雄供你选择，还有更多新英雄陆续推出！<br><br>在派对之星中，英雄被划分为均衡型、突进型、力量型、牵制型四种类型，每种类型都制作了全新的专属战斗机制。<br><strong>均衡型：通过不同方向攻击积攒能量，释放超级必杀技</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2339300/extras/98e15c6c14b7bb187319cfb74e20c134.poster.avif?t=1716944278\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2339300/extras/98e15c6c14b7bb187319cfb74e20c134.webm?t=1716944278\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2339300/extras/98e15c6c14b7bb187319cfb74e20c134.mp4?t=1716944278\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>突进型：特定招数命中后可取消硬直，制造丰富的连招可能性</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2339300/extras/ed3cd685cc0d2f459daa3e160c80fc9d.poster.avif?t=1716944278\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2339300/extras/ed3cd685cc0d2f459daa3e160c80fc9d.webm?t=1716944278\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2339300/extras/ed3cd685cc0d2f459daa3e160c80fc9d.mp4?t=1716944278\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>力量型：自身击飞值越高，拥有越高的攻击力</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2339300/extras/31a65a85e193abcebb0abe4b8a79f69e.poster.avif?t=1716944278\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2339300/extras/31a65a85e193abcebb0abe4b8a79f69e.webm?t=1716944278\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2339300/extras/31a65a85e193abcebb0abe4b8a79f69e.mp4?t=1716944278\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>牵制型：通过攻击护盾积攒能量，释放超级抓投技</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2339300/extras/5540f8fcebc57a08f6b7083c48a634d7.poster.avif?t=1716944278\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2339300/extras/5540f8fcebc57a08f6b7083c48a634d7.webm?t=1716944278\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2339300/extras/5540f8fcebc57a08f6b7083c48a634d7.mp4?t=1716944278\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>【轻松入坑】</strong><br>在月之暗面大型更新后，每周都将提供2个英雄的免费体验，可以在所有模式无限制使用！我们希望新手玩家也可以尝试多种英雄，直到你找到自己的本命英雄！全新心愿成真卡活动也可以更轻松得获得想要使用的多彩贴纸，并且首次开通完全免费！<br><br><strong>【游戏模式】</strong><br>在这里你会参与到1对1擂台、组队竞技、四人乱斗、足球模式的欢乐对战之中，另有周末限时开放的活动模式，和随时与好友对战的友谊战模式。<br>想要磨砺对战技巧的玩家，欢迎加入巅峰竞技场！在巅峰1v1、巅峰接力赛、巅峰组队赛等模式中攀升更高排名，成为派对中的大师级玩家！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2339300/extras/768d97840cf8a63da78b457cb4eba6bd.poster.avif?t=1716944278\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2339300/extras/768d97840cf8a63da78b457cb4eba6bd.webm?t=1716944278\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2339300/extras/768d97840cf8a63da78b457cb4eba6bd.mp4?t=1716944278\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>【成为冠军】</strong><br>感谢全球玩家社区的支持，能让派对之星持续举办激情且充满活力的比赛！在月之暗面大型更新中我们加入了奖杯墙功能。赢得官方赛和社区认证比赛名次，都可以在个人资料中获得比赛奖杯纪念！<br><br><strong>【个性装扮】</strong><br>收集泳池派对、东方传说、西方冒险、星际历险等多种不同主题的英雄皮肤、击飞特效和其他各类装扮，成为派对中的闪亮明星！<br><br><strong>【赛季：派对邀请函】</strong><br>每个赛季都会有独特主题的派对邀请函，参与比赛或完成赛季任务可解锁派对奖励，奖励包含皮肤、表情、击飞特效等物品。购买星光卡还能解锁更多任务，并获得兑换过往赛季限定奖励的机会。<br><br><strong>【开心社交】</strong><br>在派对中找到更多好友，和你一起组队作战或者切磋练习。组建道馆，和好友们一起切磋进步。编辑你的英雄名片，向他人展示你积累的成就。竞争英雄分数和竞技场段位的地区排行榜，成为当地数一数二的格斗高手。前往录像厅，寻找你的大神老师。在这里你有多种方式和他人一起享受欢乐的格斗派对！<br><br>闪光吧，派对之星！特别注意：虽然派对很精彩，但请不要过于着迷噢~",
